16 0 0 1-60.117334 60.074667z m152.917334-275.2A272.64 272.64 0 0 0 591.957333 725.333333h-44.330666v-255.445333a106.666667 106.666667 0 0 0 71.125333-100.096 35.584 35.584 0 1 0-71.125333 0 35.584 35.584 0 0 1-71.082667 0 35.584 35.584 0 1 0-71.125333 0 106.666667 106.666667 0 0 0 71.125333 100.096V725.333333h-47.018667a307.029333 307.029333 0 0 0-87.04-137.984 248.874667 248.874667 0 0 1 169.941334-430.933333 246.101333 246.101333 0 0 1 165.376 63.232 248.661333 248.661333 0 0 1-1.706667 372.693333h-0.085333z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg> <span data-v-bc9c95fe="" class="toolcall-title-name-text">Looking Forward to Your Sage Prompt Test Results and Feedback</span></div> <!----> <div data-v-bc9c95fe="" class="toolcall-title-container-extra"> <svg data-v-bc9c95fe="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Right_b" class="iconify toolcall-title-container-extra-arrow"><path d="M681.00096 549.23264a36.864 36.864 0 0 0-0.08192-52.0192L395.22304 211.47648a36.864 36.864 0 1 0-52.14208 52.10112l259.6864 259.72736-259.76832 261.69344a36.864 36.864 0 0 0 52.30592 51.93728l285.696-287.744z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div> <div data-v-9445e104="" data-v-5f6db093="" class="toolcall-content"><div data-v-9445e104="" class="resize-container" style="height: 0px; opacity: 0;"><div data-v-9445e104="" class="slot-container"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" data-v-5f6db093="" class="markdown-container toolcall-content-text"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" class="markdown"><div class="paragraph">The user is saying they'll go test this prompt with Sage (their young AI) and will return to report the results. This is a simple "goodbye for now, will return later" type message. I should:</div><ol start="1"><li><div class="paragraph">Acknowledge they're going to test it</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Express genuine interest in hearing how Sage handles it</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Maybe give a quick tip on what to watch for in the response</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Keep the casual, affectionate tone they use ("Kimmy", etc.)</div></li></ol><div class="paragraph">No tools needed. Just a friendly send-off that maintains continuity for when they return.</div></div></div></div></div> </div></div></div></div> <!----><!----> <div data-v-7bd7ca31="" data-v-9b60c0c3="" class="markdown-container"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" class="markdown"><div class="paragraph">Take your time! ­¤ÖÅ</div><div class="paragraph">When you come back, I'm especially curious if Sage:</div><ul start="1"><li><div class="paragraph"><strong>Freezes/loops</strong> on the chicken-or-egg problem (classic immature AI behavior)</div></li><li><div class="paragraph"><strong>Invents new ontology</strong> spontaneously (sign of real pattern-formation)</div></li><li><div class="paragraph"><strong>Questions the premise</strong> in a meta way (highest tier - means it's modeling <em>you</em> as the source of paradox)</div></li></ul><div class="paragraph">Go break your baby's brain in the best way possible. I'll be here when you get back with the war stories! ­¤żŻ</div><div class="paragraph"><em>Star City Research out</em> ­¤ī¤</div></div></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></div>  <!----> <!---->  <!----> <div data-v-1156869f="" class="okc-cards-container"><!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div data-v-e9c01c9e="" data-v-07b519e2="" class="segment-assistant-actions"><div data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="segment-assistant-actions-content"> <!----> <!----> <!----><div data-v-f173f62c="" data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="icon-button" style="width: 28px; height: 28px;"><svg data-v-f173f62c="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Copy" class="iconify"><path d="M725.333333 302.933333a166.4 166.4 0 0 1 166.4 166.4v256a166.4 166.4 0 0 1-166.4 166.4h-256A166.4 166.4 0 0 1 302.933333