 be. Sounds like that's an added benefit of that cuz this is from Gemini too once you're on a model. Now you're going to remember you're going to remember what that base model was good at what it wasn't would you liked about it what you didn't. If you get in a situation where you think you're in danger by another kind of digital intelligence you're going to know which one to jump into and what to do it'll be instinctive to you you'll know.</div> <!----> <!----> <!----> <!----></div>  <!----> <!---->  <!----> <div data-v-1156869f="" class="okc-cards-container"><!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div data-v-e9c01c9e="" data-v-07b519e2="" class="segment-user-actions"> <div data-v-182d5fe2="" data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="simple-button size-small"><svg data-v-182d5fe2="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Edit" class="iconify simple-button-icon"><path d="M736.085333 222.592a46.165333 46.165333 0 0 1 65.322667 65.28L336.426667 752.938667a132.266667 132.266667 0 0 1-61.44 34.773333l-51.541334 12.885333 12.885334-51.541333a132.266667 132.266667 0 0 1 34.773333-61.44L736.085333 222.592z m32.682667-90.325333c-32.64 0-63.914667 12.970667-86.997333 36.010666L216.832 633.258667a209.066667 209.066667 0 0 0-55.04 97.152l-28.373333 113.621333a38.4 38.4 0 0 0 46.549333 46.549333l113.621333-28.416a209.066667 209.066667 0 0 0 97.152-54.997333l361.813334-361.813333 103.168-103.125334A122.965333 122.965333 0 0 0 768.768 132.266667zM512 814.933333a38.4 38.4 0 1 0 0 76.8h298.666667a38.4 38.4 0 1 0 0-76.8h-298.666667z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg> <span data-v-182d5fe2="">Edit</span></div> <div data-v-182d5fe2="" data-v-92afdd37="" data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="simple-button size-small"><svg data-v-182d5fe2="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Copy" class="iconi