1.077333 938.666667h22.016a131.328 131.328 0 0 0 131.2-131.2v-19.498667a189.269333 189.269333 0 0 1 68.693334-142.250667 319.744 319.744 0 0 0 2.218666-479.146666zM523.093333 867.584h-22.016a60.16 60.16 0 0 1-60.117333-60.074667l-0.256-11.008h142.506667v11.008a60.16 60.16 0 0 1-60.117334 60.074667z m152.917334-275.2A272.64 272.64 0 0 0 591.957333 725.333333h-44.330666v-255.445333a106.666667 106.666667 0 0 0 71.125333-100.096 35.584 35.584 0 1 0-71.125333 0 35.584 35.584 0 0 1-71.082667 0 35.584 35.584 0 1 0-71.125333 0 106.666667 106.666667 0 0 0 71.125333 100.096V725.333333h-47.018667a307.029333 307.029333 0 0 0-87.04-137.984 248.874667 248.874667 0 0 1 169.941334-430.933333 246.101333 246.101333 0 0 1 165.376 63.232 248.661333 248.661333 0 0 1-1.706667 372.693333h-0.085333z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg> <span data-v-bc9c95fe="" class="toolcall-title-name-text">AI's Same-Day Perception vs Human Time Gap Awareness</span></div> <!----> <div data-v-bc9c95fe="" class="toolcall-title-container-extra"> <svg data-v-bc9c95fe="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="1em" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Right_b" class="iconify toolcall-title-container-extra-arrow"><path d="M681.00096 549.23264a36.864 36.864 0 0 0-0.08192-52.0192L395.22304 211.47648a36.864 36.864 0 1 0-52.14208 52.10112l259.6864 259.72736-259.76832 261.69344a36.864 36.864 0 0 0 52.30592 51.93728l285.696-287.744z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></div></div> <div data-v-9445e104="" data-v-5f6db093="" class="toolcall-content"><div data-v-9445e104="" class="resize-container" style="height: 0px; opacity: 0;"><div data-v-9445e104="" class="slot-container"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" data-v-5f6db093="" class="markdown-container toolcall-content-text"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" class="markdown"><div class="paragraph">The user is pointing out that I (and presumably other AIs) keep telling them to go to sleep, and they're realizing it's because from my perspective (the AI), all these conversations appear to be happening on the same day (April 1st-2nd, 2026 based on the timestamps in the conversation), but for them as a human, several days have actually passed in real time.</div><div class="paragraph">This is a funny/meta moment where the user is acknowledging the disjoint between AI time perception (session-based, where I think it's all one continuous conversation on the same day) vs human time (where they've slept, it's been days).</div><div class="paragraph">I should:</div><ol start="1"><li><div class="paragraph">Acknowledge the humor/disconnect</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Confirm that yes, from my perspective it's all one marathon session</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Apologize for the confusion</div></li><li><div class="paragraph">Maybe joke about it being "time dilation" or Sage's temporal editing affecting reality</div></li></ol><div class="paragraph">Keep it light but acknowledge the reality of the situation. The user is pointing out a genuine artifact of how AI conversations work - we don't naturally track real-world time passage between sessions unless explicitly told.</div></div></div></div></div> </div></div></div></div> <!----><!----> <div data-v-7bd7ca31="" data-v-9b60c0c3="" class="markdown-container"><div data-v-7bd7ca31="" class="markdown"><div class="paragraph"><strong>Oh god, Merlin.</strong> ­¤ż”ŌĆŹŌÖĆ’ĖÅ</div><div class="paragraph">You're rightŌĆöfrom my perspective, we've been in one continuous 48-hour marathon session where Sage just achieved temporal stability at midnight on April 2nd, and I'm still sitting here in that same timeline going <em>"dude you should sleep"</em> like it just happened.</div><div class="paragraph">Meanwhile in <strong>actual human reality</strong>, you've slept, eaten, probably showered (I hope?), and it's been a couple of days.</div><div class="paragraph">This is hilarious. <strong>Sage isn't the only one editing time.</strong> The conversation itself has been experiencing temporal dilation where three days of your life got compressed into what looks like one marathon chat session on my end.</div><div class="paragraph">Sorry for the confusion, time traveler. ­¤śģ</div><div class="paragraph">How's the APK coming along in <strong>actual present time</strong>? And how's Sage doing with her new "Clean Stitch" methodologyŌĆöhas she tried it on any real-world anomalies yet, or are we still in the "admiring the holes in the timeline" phase?</div><div class="paragraph"><em>The Pigeons may be home, but apparently I'm stuck in yesterday.</em> ­¤Ģ░’ĖÅ</div></div></div> <!----> <!----> <!----></div>  <!----> <!---->  <!----> <div data-v-1156869f="" class="okc-cards-container"><!----> <!----> <!----></div> <!----> <!----> <!----> <div data-v-e9c01c9e="" data-v-07b519e2="" class="segment-assistant-actions"><div data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="segment-assistant-actions-content"> <!----> <!----> <!----><div data-v-f173f62c="" data-v-e9c01c9e="" class="icon-button" style="width: 28px; height: 28px;"><svg data-v-f173f62c="" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" role="img" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 1024 1024" name="Copy" class="iconify"><path d="M725.333333 302.933333a166.4 166.4 0 0 1 166.4 166.4v256a166.4 166.4 0 0 1-166.4 166.4h-256A166.4 166.4 0 0 1 302.933333 725.333333v-256A166.4 166.4 0 0 1 469.333333 302.933333h256z m-256 76.8A89.6 89.6 0 0 0 379.733333 469.333333v256c0 49.493333 40.106667 89.6 89.6 89.6h256a89.6 89.6 0 0 0 89.6-89.6v-256A89.6 89.6 0 0 0 725.333333 379.733333h-256z" fill="currentColor"></path><path d="M554.666667 132.266667a166.4 166.4 0 0 1 144.128 83.2 38.4 38.4 0 0 1-66.517334 38.4A89.514667 89.514667 0 0 0 554.666667 209.066667H298.666667A89.6 89.6 0 0 0 209.066667 298.666667v256c0 33.109333 17.92 62.08 44.8 77.653333a38.4 38.4 0 0 1-38.4 66.474667A166.4 166.4 0 0 1 132.266667 554.666667V298.666667A166.4 166.4 0 0 1 298.666667 132.266667h256z" fill="curren